<td><span style="text-align: center;">信达生物</span></td>
<td><span style="text-align: center;">信迪利单抗</span></td>
<td><span style="text-align: center;">达伯舒</span></td>
<td><span style="text-align: center;">9.21亿元</span></td>
<td><span style="text-align: center;">9.7万</span></td>
