<td><span style="text-align: center;">卡瑞利珠单抗</span></td>
<td><span style="text-align: center;">艾瑞卡</span></td>
<td><span style="text-align: center;">超20亿元</span></td>
<td><span style="text-align: center;">赠药前12万</span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><span style="text-align: center;">百济神州</span></td>
<td><span style="text-align: center;">替雷利珠单抗</span></td>
<td><span style="text-align: center;">百泽安</span></td>
<td><span style="text-align: center;">3.5亿元</span></td>
<td><span style="text-align: center;">3个月8.5万</span></td>
